"""
List View Customization:
- list_display: Fields/methods to show in list
- list_filter: Filters in sidebar
- search_fields: Fields to search
- ordering: Default ordering
- list_editable: Fields editable in list view
- list_per_page: Items per page
- date_hierarchy: Date-based navigation

Detail View Customization:
- fields: Fields to show (simple layout)
- fieldsets: Organized sections
- readonly_fields: Non-editable fields
- prepopulated_fields: Auto-fill from other fields
- autocomplete_fields: Autocomplete for FK/M2M
- raw_id_fields: Raw ID for FK/M2M

Actions:
- actions: List of custom actions
- @admin.action: Decorator for action methods

Permissions:
- has_add_permission(): Control add permission
- has_change_permission(): Control edit permission
- has_delete_permission(): Control delete permission
- has_view_permission(): Control view permission

Queryset Optimization:
- get_queryset(): Customize queryset
- select_related(): For FK/OneToOne
- prefetch_related(): For M2M/reverse FK
- annotate(): Add computed fields

Inlines:
- TabularInline: Compact table layout
- StackedInline: Full field layout
- extra: Number of empty forms
- max_num: Maximum forms

Display Methods:
- @admin.display: Decorator for custom columns
- description: Column header
- ordering: Enable sorting
- boolean: Show as boolean icon
- short_description: (deprecated, use @admin.display)

Filters:
- SimpleListFilter: Custom filter class
- lookups(): Define filter options
- queryset(): Apply filter logic
"""
